{% block subject %}
    {% spaceless %}
        Majority-to-Minority Transfer Status for Confirmation Number: {{ submission.confirmationNumber }}
    {% endspaceless %}
{% endblock subject %}

{% block body_text %}
Hi {{ submission.email }},

Guardian of {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }}

RE: Majority-to-Minority Transfer Status for Confirmation Number: {{ submission.confirmationNumber }}

The {{ submission.enrollmentPeriod }} Majority-to-Minority Round 2 Lottery has been completed. Your application for a Majority-to-Minority Student Transfer for {{ submission.firstName }} {{ submission.lastName }} for {{ submission.enrollmentPeriod }} was not awarded a space and has been wait listed for the following choice:

{{ waitListedSchool.formattedString }}

Should additional spaces become available at {{ waitListedSchool.formattedString }}, those spaces will be filled by students on the Wait List based on each student’s lottery number.  If spaces become available at {{ waitListedSchool.formattedString }} and your student is selected for a space based on his/her lottery number, our office will contact you and award your student a space at this school. Please note that the Wait List expires on July 15, {{ submission.enrollmentPeriod.afterLotteryEndingDate|date("Y") }}.

Please save this email and/or record this confirmation number for your records.

Please add choice@tusc.k12.al.us to your address list to ensure you receive future status updates of your application.

This is an automated email message from a mailbox that does not accept replies. If you have any questions regarding the Majority-to-Minority student transfer process, please contact TCS Attendance Office.

Thanks,
Tuscaloosa City Schools
{% endblock body_text %}

